Detailed Description

cvmx_pnb::_ppcmd_ff_dbe_info

This register contains information on double-bit ECC errors that occured in the command FIFO for cnMIPS requests to SMEM. These correspond to PNB(0..1)_INT_SUM[MEM11_DBE] interrupts.
